{
  "id": "adv_card_chs_08_02",
  "title": "白石千紗 2話 一緒に頑張ろうね",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_lesson-02-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――レッスン当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――The day of the lesson.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_02-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "すぅー……ふぅー……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sighー… Phewー…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 1.9666666051,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "緊張してるみたいだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You seem nervous.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.3666666051,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_02-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ……ちょっとだけ……\n練習はしてきましたけど、やっぱり心配で",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ehehe… Just a little…\nI practiced‚ but I’m still worried.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.8999999385,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_02-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "でも、今日は頑張るって決めましたから\nだから、大丈夫です！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I’ve decided to do my best today.\nSo I’ll be okay!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.6999999385,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そうか。じゃあ、そろそろ入ってきてもらうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay. Shall I have her come in?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.1230386913,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9176.959975500002,
          "startTime": 33.2999986668
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9676.959975500002,
          "startTime": 33.7999986668
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_02-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　お願いします！\n――どうぞ、入って下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes! Please!\n――Please come in.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.3999999385,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（もうすぐ中学生くらいの女の子だな）\n（千紗に会えて凄く嬉しそうだ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（She’s about to be a middle schooler.）\n（She looks really happy to meet Chisa.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.4333320002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_02-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "こ、こんにちは。本日レッスンを担当する白石千紗です\n……よろしくね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "H-hello. I’m Shiraishi Chisa‚ and I’ll be in charge of your lesson today.\nIt’s nice to meet you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.1999986668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（教えることに慣れていないせいか）\n（まだ少し緊張しているみたいだな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（She still seems a bit nervous）\n（because she’s not used to teaching.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.643107432,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_02-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "ファンレター、ありがとう。今日は先生として\nがんびゃ……が、頑張らせてもらうね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you for your fan letter. Today‚ as your teacher‚\nI’ll dyu… I'll do my best!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.0000019729,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_02-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "うぅ……噛んじゃった……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Uuu… I messed up…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.3790941257,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "千紗、落ち着いて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Chisa‚ calm down.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.1124274591,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_02-chs008.m4a",
      "text": "ご、ごめんなさい！\nリラックス……リラックス……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "S-sorry!\nRelax… relax…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.5000019729,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_02-chs009.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃあ、まずはあなたの\nダンスを見せてもらってもいいかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay‚ then‚ first‚\ncould you show me your dance?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.3666686396,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4261.223943900006,
          "startTime": 80.6278925835
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（うん、始めたばかりだと聞いていたが）\n（結構うまいんじゃないか？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Hmm‚ I heard she just started）\n（but she’s pretty good?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.8666686396,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_02-chs010.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう。躍動感があっていい感じだね\nステップも上手で……え？　か、改善点……！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you. That was nice and dynamic.\nYour steps were good too… Eh? F-Feedback…!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.2000019729,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_02-chs011.m4a",
      "text": "えっと……う、動きが少し『イビルハザード』の\nメタルゾンビみたいになってるかな！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um… well… your movements were a bit like the\nmetal zombies in \"Evil Hazard\"!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.3666686396,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（千紗！？）\n（急によく分からない例えになってるぞ！？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Chisa!?）\n（You’re suddenly making strange comparisons!?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.5000106196,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_02-chs012.m4a",
      "text": "ご、ごめんね、分かり辛いよね！？\n聞かれると思ってなくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "S-sorry‚ that was hard to understand‚ wasn’t it!?\nI wasn’t expecting to be asked that…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.1333439529,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_02-chs013.m4a",
      "text": "と、とにかく、少し肩の力を抜いてもいいのかな……\nなんて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A-anyway‚ it is okay to take it easy a little…\nmaybe…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.5000106196,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_02-chs014.m4a",
      "text": "えっと……と、とりあえず、今のを踏まえて\nもう一度踊ってもらえるかな……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um… w-well‚ for now‚ based on my advice‚\ncould you dance it again…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.8333439529,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_02-chs015.m4a",
      "text": "ここの振り付けが苦手なの？\nえっと、今だと、そうだね……うぅ、なんて言えば……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you having trouble with this choreography?\nUm‚ right now‚ yeah… Uuu‚ how should I put this…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.3000121455,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（千紗、言葉を選ぼうとし過ぎるあまり）\n（テンパってるみたいだな……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Chisa is trying so hard to choose the right words）\n（that she's freaking out…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.6000045776,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "二人とも\nずっと続けているし、この辺で少し休憩しようか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay‚ you two.\nWe’ve been at it for a while‚ so let’s take a break.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.5000121455,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_02-chs016.m4a",
      "text": "ご、ごめんなさい……\nひとまず休憩して、また再開しましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "S-sorry…\nLet’s take a break and then start again.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.7000121455,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 157.9796030301
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 157.9796030301
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_02-chs017.m4a",
      "text": "うぅ……私、全然ダメでした……\n{user}さんとも練習したのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Uuu… I was terrible…\nEven after I practiced with {user}-san…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 164.7000121455,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "本番でうまくいかないことは、誰にでもあるさ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone can make mistakes at the important moments.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167.7629261909,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 171.3019967017
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_08_02-chs018.m4a",
      "text": "でも……やっぱり私よりも\n怜ちゃんの方が適任だったんじゃ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But… maybe Rei-chan\nwould have been better suited for this…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 174.7333454788,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
