      "text": "誰よりも努力家で、何度挫けても立ち上がってきた\nそんな千紗の努力はファンにも伝わってると思う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You've worked harder than others‚ and got back up whenever you fell.\nSo‚ I think fans would recognize your efforts.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 197.3333566686,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
