      "text": "自分の好きなこととか、得意なことを知ることも\n大切だと思うの。その方が、楽しく続けられるかなって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I think it’s also important to know what you like and\nwhat you’re good at. It would make it more fun to keep going‚ you know?",
        "id": ""
